p1_ort_base¶

namespace Ort
class P1OrtBase : public Ort::OrtBase¶
#include <p1_ort_base.hpp>

An Precision-Level 1 (P1) ONNXRuntime (Ort) Base class object. This class object instantiates a Precision Level 1 Ort Session which takes a typical ONNX model used for solely image classification and runs an inferenc engine.
